                <div class="help-section-icon"><i class="bi bi-cart3"></i></div>
                <div>
                    <div class="help-section-title">Purchases</div>
                    <div class="help-section-desc">Recording new book acquisitions and supplier invoices.</div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="help-card">
                <div class="help-card-head">
                    <div class="help-card-head-left">
                        <div class="help-card-num">1</div>
                        <div class="help-card-label">Creating a Purchase</div>
                    </div>
                    <i class="bi bi-chevron-down help-card-chevron"></i>
                </div>
                <div class="help-card-body">
                    <p>Go to <strong>Purchases → Create</strong>. Enter the supplier, invoice number, and purchase date. Add line items for each catalog being purchased, specifying quantity and unit price. Saving a purchase automatically increases the stock counts in the related catalogs.</p>
                </div>
