                <div class="help-card-body">
                    <p>Library logs record when a student or visitor reads a book inside the library without borrowing it. Go to <strong>Library Logs → Create</strong>, select the student, add the books read, and save. The log goes through an Approval → Return workflow managed by staff.</p>
