        <div class="help-section" id="sec-users">
            <div class="help-section-header">
                <div class="help-section-icon"><i class="bi bi-person-gear"></i></div>
                <div>
                    <div class="help-section-title">Users & Roles</div>
                    <div class="help-section-desc">Managing staff accounts and access permissions.</div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="help-card">
                <div class="help-card-head">
                    <div class="help-card-head-left">
                        <div class="help-card-num">1</div>
                        <div class="help-card-label">Creating a Staff User</div>
                    </div>
                    <i class="bi bi-chevron-down help-card-chevron"></i>
                </div>
                <div class="help-card-body">
                    <p>Go to <strong>Users → Create</strong>. Enter the full name, email, and password, then assign a role. Roles control which modules the user can access. Only admins can create or modify users.</p>
