        <div class="help-section" id="sec-account">
            <div class="help-section-header">
                <div class="help-section-icon"><i class="bi bi-shield-lock"></i></div>
                <div>
                    <div class="help-section-title">Account & Security</div>
                    <div class="help-section-desc">Managing your profile and password.</div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="help-card">
                <div class="help-card-head">
                    <div class="help-card-head-left">
                        <div class="help-card-num">1</div>
                        <div class="help-card-label">Updating Your Profile</div>
                    </div>
                    <i class="bi bi-chevron-down help-card-chevron"></i>
                </div>
                <div class="help-card-body">
                    <p>Click your profile photo in the top navbar and select <strong>Profile</strong>. You can update your full name, email, and profile picture. Changes take effect immediately after saving.</p>
